Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Chizuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema Torazou has been murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and both of his arms were severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mikagura Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: Tamesuu & akutsu | Timing: PlasticYakuza | Editing: Collectr | Typeset & Encode: ShocWave | QC: Brush
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, Tomoe-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boobs are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you mess around like this, we'll be late to\Nour appointment with Inspector Morimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought that Nema\NTorazou would be murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this puts us right back where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Tomoe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind letting go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. It's just that they're so perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me just because Shigeno-san's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, she still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a call saying she was staying at\Nher brother Shizuto-san's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drop by later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll savor this feeling one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,– No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,– Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Shigeno-san doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She cried herself to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so you two can continue the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any clues at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you come out here for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that other girl who was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... She wasn't feeling very well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to talk to her about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess I'll contact her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if we learn anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, there is something that's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms... His arms are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness seemed shocked that\NTorazou's arms had been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of the tattoos he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tattoos?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema Torazou had tattoos on both his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They were supposed to bring him good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People around here really believe in that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who'd actually be\Nupset about Torazou's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mimasaka Sue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue? I heard she started working\Nat a different shop yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you were free to come and go\Nwas that you were Torazou's woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it to stay that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep your privileges,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you will obey me. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make you my woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to keep that inside you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been watching us for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So why were you following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ordered you to follow us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his little sister Houran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, that's right. She's my sister Houran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking care of Tokito-san right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've moved the detective to another\Nlocation so he can fully recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Houran's been looking after him in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you have any messages for\NTokito, she can deliver them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said so sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was just embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the shy type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I get the feeling I've\Nseen you somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for playing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As your reward, I'll punish you\Nto your heart's content today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The new priest, Kaburagi-san, seems\Nlike a kind and dedicated person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife is very nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mimasaka Sue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go and talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She got away from us last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, Sue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're arguing over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does seeing me bother you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's money you want, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she treat her own flesh and blood that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Her older brother was brutally murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she'd be devastated, so I came to console her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. Did you just say her brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatanaka Reiji-san. He was the priest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatanaka-san was Mimasaka Sue's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't believe it. I won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a terrible woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still feel the same way about Tokito-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama, you've been here this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been the same since you were small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When something didn't go your way,\Nyou'd cry, cry, and cry some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'd get tired of crying and fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'd never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now matter how much you were scolded,\Nyou did what you believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the same way when you said\Nyou wanted to work for Tokito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but be envious of your persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of problems\Nyou encountered along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you always followed through on your decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to have a sister like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to keep investigating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a member of the Mikagura Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Houran really is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the long faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, how is Tokito-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Sensei is still recovering.\NWe were about to go visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have to go see Morimatsu-san right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the expression of a man\Nwho's obtained what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Hayasumi-san, a government\Nofficial, covering my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Torazou couldn't get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise, Hayasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, greet our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a welcome sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayasumi Renji, the undersecretary\Nfor local business liaisons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the poster child for selfish self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful about what you say, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for one, support your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's what I wanted to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is trying to get my brother demoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, your brother is very vigilant when it comes\Nto other bureaucrats being involved in fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That does sound like my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Hayasumi's been seen at Kotora a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that since Torazou died,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been especially persistent about getting\Nyour brother dismissed from his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Hayasumi be the one who murdered Torazou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, we'd have arrested him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do know that he's teamed\Nup with Kotojiro from Kotora,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and that they're now plotting something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that related to Hatanaka-san's murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hayasumi Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Now everything is starting to make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before Hatanaka\Nand Torazou's murders are solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have another go at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bad neighborhood, so stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you. Let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've done great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one more job for you, Ranmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Sensei. There's just one small matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
