Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You look cute like that, so what's the harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you're right. I'm off then!
