Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find Hayasumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayasumi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to expose this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't, I won't be able to face them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of interest in this place lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumiyama and the girls aren't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this a lasting relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and show Hayasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by the taste that she\Ncomes from a good household.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What would your brother think if he saw you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave my brother out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act tough. Your brother brought\Nit on himself by being too righteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do anything to my brother, I'll, never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you see how your precious brother\Nbecomes an outcast of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's leave the chatting at that and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,– No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you prefer the tighter hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her a taste of that thick dick of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me, Onii-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A lady's a lot tighter than your common tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna cum already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shooting it inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a go at her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's ready for you up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send both you and your brother to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You... bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.30,0:24:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-sama! I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.26,0:24:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayasumi-san, we'll need you to explain\Nyourself at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.50,0:24:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue-san. Were you the one who killed Torazou,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.58,0:24:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and cut off his arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.14,0:25:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.10,0:25:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the one who killed Hatanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.70,0:25:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sue wouldn't kill Hatanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.78,0:25:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in love with Hatanaka-san, and he with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.38,0:25:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.94,0:25:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't Christianity forbid suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct. And that's exactly why he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure he didn't receive God's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.58,0:25:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We were separated from each\Nother when we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When my brother was old enough\Nto work, my mother sold him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.21,0:25:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And later, she sold me to Torazou.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.86,0:25:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when my life turned into a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.42,0:25:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Torazou made me his mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.14,0:25:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He treated me like a sex toy, day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:25:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around that time that I found my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.86,0:26:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and I fell in love without\Nrealizing we were siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.14,0:26:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned he was my brother from the suicide\Nnote he left after slitting his own throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.58,0:26:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Torazou was the one who told my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was using that information to blackmail my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you cut off Hatanaka-san's arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.74,0:26:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want everyone to know\Nthat he committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.86,0:26:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted people to remember\Nhim as a righteous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.58,0:26:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you killed Torazou and\Ncut off his arms for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.86,0:26:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.86,0:26:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherish your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.78,0:27:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will.
