Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.45,0:27:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.26,0:27:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still the man who's been pulling all the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hoshi no tame nara then you mou sorenai
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If the stars have decided it then I can't avoid you.
