Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.90,0:28:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes give nothing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.14,0:28:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kurakura suru youna koi ni inochi wo kezuri
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.14,0:28:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A dizzying love whittles away at my life.
