Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.42,0:28:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I store my confused memories in the\Nblackness of scars and my shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.70,0:28:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hai no tamago no nani mo kowakunai
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.70,0:28:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of in an egg of ash.
